    "description": "In a quest to break the curse, a lone traveller must reach the heart of the Forbidden Capital to unleash the power of the Ancient Source.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CURSED CHARACTER</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You must select a <strong>curse </strong>for your new character at creation.<br></li><li>The selected <strong>curse </strong>is heavily influnces your playthrough, so choose wisely. </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829560/extras/ce5abe69b852fa8a74d393ae9eeeb51b.avif?t=1673381032\" width=600 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829560/extras/f05539acfbb7a0c554b7f37cbb6739d5.avif?t=1673381032\" width=600 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829560/extras/9ecc16de9a8c72edb6fb0a32f7e6917a.avif?t=1673381032\" width=600 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829560/extras/9e8524e220440ecf4fc20ba30c4fc496.avif?t=1673381032\" width=600 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829560/extras/b0ebb78680d3b5a51bbc42790091d28a.avif?t=1673381032\" width=600 height=64 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZE YOUR PLAYSTYLE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Define </strong>your playstyle with your class, as every class has its own unique trait and attribute distribution.<br></li><li><strong>Customize </strong>your active abilities, weapons, and gear.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829560/extras/125b633fe678f93449b7dce9339125cf.avif?t=1673381032\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PROCEDURALLY GENERATED CITY</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Every playthrough is different.<br></li><li><strong>Explore </strong>a vast procedurally generated city full of enemies, loot and hidden passages.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVAL MECHANICS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Scavenge </strong>for resources.<br></li><li>Deal with sanity, hunger and thirst while trying to survive. </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEADLY NIGHT</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Find </strong>a monolith before nightfall as the night is dark and full of terrors.<br></li><li>Monoliths will keep you safe, surviving the night is hopeless without them.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SETTLEMENTS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Settlements built around mysterious monoliths are the last safe places in the capital.<br></li><li><strong>Interact </strong>with NPCs like traders, blacksmiths and weapon masters.<br></li><li><strong>Learn </strong>new abilities, buy new equipment or upgrade your existing gear.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829560/extras/aee0084af2bec1aef18060ded8f79dd7.webp?t=1673381032\" width=600 height=5 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THE DEVELOPER</h2>I am <strong>NECROW</strong> a <strong>solo developer</strong>, the only creator of NECROBLADE.<br><br>If you have any questions or suggestions, please join the <strong>Official Discord server</strong> or follow me @devNecrow on <strong>Twitter</strong>.<br><br>Also if you want to support the project, please <strong>WISHLIST </strong>and <strong>FOLLOW </strong>the game on Steam.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829560/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1673381032\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829560/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1673381032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829560/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1673381032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
